Let $$M \subseteq \{\,(u,v) \in \R^2 \mid v > 1\,\}$$ and
$$
f\colon M \to \R^3, \quad
f(u,v) \coloneqq \begin{pmatrix}
  \cos(u)/v \\
  \sin(u)/v \\
  \log(\sqrt{v^2-1}+v) - \frac{\sqrt{v^2-1}}{v}
\end{pmatrix}.
$$